Class Pair<E,F>

  • java.lang.Object
    • teo.isgci.util.Pair<E,F>

  • public class Pair<E,F>
extends java.lang.Object
    A Pair is an object that contains two other objects. It is most commonly used for conveniently storing and passing pairs of objects.
